<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Activate to display the bank details in the order process and the order history. For further information, refer to <a href="/en/payment/managing-bank-details#40">Displaying bank details in order process</a>.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Show designated use</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Activate to display the designated use in the order process and the order history. For further information, refer to <a href="/en/payment/managing-bank-details#40">Displaying bank details in order process</a>.</p></td>
</tr>
